title: Microsoft Office Professional Plus 2013 (English, Traditional Ch
description:
1 Must remove the old version before installation. 

2 This is a set of programs for traditional and simplified Chinese, English, X86 and X64 individual separate image file, simply select the desired version for installation. 

3 You can click on the map to enter the product key, and enter MH2KN-96KYR-GTRD4-KBKP4-Q9JP9 to start, but can not be verified, extended time to 30 days. 

4 KMSmicro v3.10 is attached for activation. Please refer to Readme !!.txt.
